After much contemplation during high school on what career I would pursue, I chose business as it has run in my family. However, I wanted to diversify a little and get into something that not all ordinary business majors would dip their hands in. I've played video games and used computers all my life so I figured that MIS would be a great way to do this while I attend Shidler. 
